Class LoginPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • LoginPage
  • public class LoginPage
extends java.lang.Object
    LoginPage class for the website https://www.saucedemo.com/ The LoginPage class represents the page where users can log in. It contains methods to interact with the login form elements.
